{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_04_02",
  "title": "kana",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんが映画に出演することになり）\n（本格的にミーティングや稽古が始まった……のだが）",
      "startTime": 3.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ふざっけんな！！\nな～にが『大ヒット人情コメディ、待望の実写化』よ！",
      "startTime": 10.7266667684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "台本の九割はくっだらないギャグと汚い言葉じゃん！\n三ページごとに『クソ』って言ってるんですけど！？",
      "startTime": 18.4333330154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それでも原作は数千万部の大ヒットなんですよ……",
      "startTime": 21.4836956024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "しかもkanaがあんな役とか聞いてない！！",
      "startTime": 25.7253743172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざkanaにオファーしてくるなら\nてっきり、可愛いヒロインだと思ったのに！",
      "startTime": 31.4666663487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "コッテコテの広島弁のヒットマンって……\n昭和の任侠映画かっての、パクり以前に古過ぎるわ！",
      "startTime": 39.0666663487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "年中お尻かいてるし、飲んだくれてるし、血も吐くし\n大体出てきて三ページ後には車に轢かれてるし！",
      "startTime": 48.4999996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "どう見ても出オチのネタキャラじゃん！\nkanaのイメージと全ッ然違くない！？",
      "startTime": 54.4999996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（そう、kanaさんは絶対嫌がるだろうと思った）\n（だから俺の方で断っておくつもりだったんだが……）",
      "startTime": 61.8999996821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "あと気に食わないのがさぁ、ド貧乏って設定ね\nfranにやらせとけっての、そんな役！",
      "startTime": 70.1333279292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんがドッキリに出たのを、監督が観ていて\nあのリアクションがいい！　と感銘を受けたそうで……",
      "startTime": 76.366655159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、そうなんだ\nやっぱkanaってバラエティでも無敵だし？",
      "startTime": 82.9999884923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "って、そんなんで騙されるか！\nkanaはアイドルで、芸人じゃないっつーの！！",
      "startTime": 89.5999884923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました。今からでも断りましょう\n情報公開前なので、変更はギリギリ可能かと……",
      "startTime": 96.6333233516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "は？　何バカ言ってんの\nこんな大きい仕事、やるに決まってるでしょ",
      "startTime": 104.4333233516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "大ヒット作の映画化だよ？\nこんな目立てるチャンス、滅多にないし",
      "startTime": 110.1333233516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "主演も全部食って\nkanaの映画にしてやるんだから！",
      "startTime": 115.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "これで実績作って、ゴールデンタイムのドラマに出て\nお茶の間のテレビをkanaで埋め尽くしてやる！",
      "startTime": 121.5333243688,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5289.636294400012,
          "startTime": 126.8229606632
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5533.342297900006,
          "startTime": 127.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 125.6229616805,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5277.038319500008,
          "startTime": 130.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-noon",
      "startTime": 126.7229606632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、みなさん休憩中みたいですね\n……あれ、kanaさん、何を読んでるんですか？",
      "startTime": 132.1333233516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "見りゃ分かるでしょ\n例の映画の原作に目を通してんの",
      "startTime": 138.0666566849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "なんせ七十巻以上あるからさぁ\n時間ある時に読まないと、読み終わらないんだよね",
      "startTime": 144.3666515987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "かなりの巻数ですけど、誰かに借りたんですか？",
      "startTime": 148.6702572509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "山田さんは全巻持ってるらしいけど\n借り作るのイヤだから自分で買った",
      "startTime": 156.2333182653,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5091.685342299997,
          "startTime": 161.3250036076
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8313.348401399991,
          "startTime": 164.5466666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "はは……本人がいる所で言わなくても……\nスリクスは相変わらずですね",
      "startTime": 163.8666526159,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9533.347384100012,
          "startTime": 173.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "漫画の実写化って、数字はそこそこ出るけど\nSNSで叩かれることも多いし",
      "startTime": 170.3666526159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、こっちが原作舐めてるとだけは\n思われないようにしないと……",
      "startTime": 176.2666526159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、トリエルの優って漫画好きなんでしょ\n即売会？　に出たとか話題になってたし",
      "startTime": 182.599984932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、前に同人誌を作ってましたね",
      "startTime": 186.7300918424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "この漫画の評判とか、kanaのやるキャラが\nどんなとこが人気かとか、聞いてきて",
      "startTime": 193.9999788285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "優なら、レッスン後に事務所に寄るって言ってましたし\n聞けば普通に教えてくれると思いますけど",
      "startTime": 200.7666454952,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9866.696993399984,
          "startTime": 210.6333424886
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-kan022.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの子達、スリクス嫌いでしょ\nどの面下げて来やがったって思われたくないもん",
      "startTime": 206.8333121618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_04_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさん、仕事には本当に熱心だよなあ……）\n（出オチのネタキャラだって、あんなに嫌がってたのに）",
      "startTime": 217.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 222.1334303066,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
